"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-olympics-2024-sky-brown-skateboarding-surfing-b1175155.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  Sky Brownbattled to a brave bronze in Tuesday's skateboarding park final, then immediately set her sights on becoming a two-sport Olympian in Los Angeles in four years' time.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999969718374, \"rank\": 3.027997675865679e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 387, \"end\": 398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999721981115, \"rank\": 2.513869374952689e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brown overcame a heavy qualifying fall on the shoulder she had dislocated less than a fortnight ago tomake the podium for the second time, becoming the youngestTeam GBathlete to win medals at multipleOlympic Games.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 16-year-old, who will now undergo surgery on her shoulder, also attempted to qualify for thesurfingat the2024 Olympics, competing at the World Surfing Games in Puerto Rico in March.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 801, \"end\": 812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"score\": 0.9998526125828421, \"rank\": 0.00014726463141184672, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Doing so may have been a logistical impossibility in any case, given the women's medals were only awarded in the early hours of Tuesday morning, almost 10,000 miles away from Paris, in Tahiti.\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999989386197, \"rank\": 1.0613028611484894e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999395459342579, \"rank\": 6.036118466434152e-05, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That, though, is unlikely to be an issue in LA and Brown, who spends much of her time in California, is desperate to be in action on two boards.\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.999558685066252, \"rank\": 0.0004329983803934512, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024 medal table and latest count today  Olympics 2024: Every Team GB medal winner at the Paris Games so far  \\\"I am a double Olympic medallist,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's really cool and I am very happy.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1366, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I go to LA, I am hoping to be a double Olympian there in surfing and skating.\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1411, \"end\": 1419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999969718374, \"rank\": 3.027997675865679e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every time I lose, I learn, and I learn a lot every day and I can bring that to LA.\\\"\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1534, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are, however, other tasks for the teenager to tick off before then.\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have some school work to do,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can get my driver's licence in America.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I miss surfing right now, so I am hoping to get into the water straight away.\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I need to get a shoulder surgery, but hopefully that will not take too long.\\\"\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brown's participation in the final had at one stage looked in doubt, with the youngster in obvious discomfort when leaving the course at the end of qualifying.\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterwards, her father, Stewart, revealed she had effectively dislocated her shoulder again.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2043, \"end\": 2050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Stuart\", \"score\": 0.5472892140079028, \"rank\": 0.7456780287699601, \"text\": \"Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Stuart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Stuart\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It came out and popped back in,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She did not even tell [the medical staff] it came out, because she was afraid they would pull her out.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I ran down to her and she said, 'Daddy, it's come out'.\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, as we were getting up, she said, 'Oh, I think it's gone back in'.\\\"\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Remarkably, Brown was the oldest member of a podium that was headed by 14-year-old Australian Arisa Trew, with 15-year-old Japanese Cocona Hiraki taking silver.\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2473, \"end\": 2483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.999696045947231, \"rank\": 0.00020266204467751786, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 2484, \"end\": 2489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0331800512905924e-17, \"text\": \"Arisa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\"}, {\"begin\": 2513, \"end\": 2521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.7402286999860198, \"rank\": 0.3467531942653185, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The contrast on Wednesday afternoon, then, will be stark, when 51-year-old Andy MacDonald, a multiple X Games gold medalist, makes his Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2627, \"end\": 2641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"score\": 0.7012169389860421, \"rank\": 0.42608695652174866, \"text\": \"Andy MacDonald\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Honestly, I do not understand half of the tricks he does,\\\" Brown said of her team-mate.\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I definitely need some tips from him.\\\"\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2831, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 3711,